msgid ""
"macOS: `~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`"
msgstr ""
"macOS：`~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:129
msgid "Windows: `%APPDATA%\\Claude\\claude_desktop_config.json`"
msgstr "Windows：`%APPDATA%\\Claude\\claude_desktop_config.json`"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:130
msgid "Linux: `~/.config/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`"
msgstr "Linux：`~/.config/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:132
msgid "**Configuration:**"
msgstr "**配置：**"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:145
msgid "**Example with actual path:**"
msgstr "**实际路径示例：**"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:158
msgid "**Important:** Restart Claude Desktop after configuration changes."
msgstr "**重要：**修改配置后重启 Claude Desktop。"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:162
msgid "Other MCP Clients"
msgstr "其他 MCP 客户端"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:164
msgid "For other MCP-compatible clients:"
msgstr "对于其他兼容 MCP 的客户端："

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:166
msgid ""
"**Find Python path:** Activate virtual environment and run `which python`"
msgstr "**找到 Python 路径：**激活虚拟环境并运行 `which python`"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:167
msgid "**Use in configuration:** Replace `\"python\"` with the full path"
msgstr "**写入配置：**用完整路径替换 `\"python\"`"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:169
msgid ""
"ChatSpatial follows the standard MCP protocol and works with any MCP-"
"compatible client."
msgstr "ChatSpatial 遵循标准 MCP 协议，可在任何兼容 MCP 的客户端中使用。"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:173
msgid "Environment Variables (Optional)"
msgstr "环境变量（可选）"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:175
msgid "Configure ChatSpatial behavior using environment variables:"
msgstr "使用环境变量配置 ChatSpatial 行为："

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:177
msgid "Data Storage"
msgstr "数据存储"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:184
msgid ""
"**Usage:** When you use `export_data()` without specifying `path`, datasets "
"are saved to this directory."
msgstr ""
"**用途：**当你使用 `export_data()` 且未指定 `path` 时，数据集会保存到该目录。"

#: ../../advanced/configuration.md:186
msgid "**Default:** `.chatspatial_saved/` next to original data file"
msgstr "**默认：**在原始数据文件旁的 `.chatspatial_saved/`"

